### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5120
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get all municipalities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/municipalities

### Create a new municipality
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/municipalities
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "nombre": "Poza Rica",
  "estado": "Veracruz"
}

### Get municipality by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/municipalities/1

### Get all settlements
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/settlements

### Create a new settlement
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/settlements
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "nombre": "Centro",
  "municipioId": 1,
  "tipoAsentamiento": "Colonia",
  "ambito": "Urbano"
}

### Get settlements by municipality
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/settlements/by-municipality/1

### Get all shelters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shelters

### Create a new shelter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shelters
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "nombre": "Albergue Central Poza Rica",
  "direccion": "Calle Principal 123, Centro",
  "municipioId": 1,
  "capacidadMaxima": 100,
  "responsable": "Juan Pérez",
  "fechaApertura": "2024-10-12T00:00:00"
}

### Get available shelters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shelters/available

### Get all persons (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/persons?page=1&pageSize=10

### Search persons
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/persons/search?query=Juan

### Create a new person
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/persons
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "nombre": "María",
  "apellidoPaterno": "González",
  "apellidoMaterno": "López",
  "edad": 35,
  "sexo": "F",
  "municipioId": 1,
  "asentamientoNombre": "Centro"
}

### Assign person to shelter
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/persons/1/assign-shelter
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

1

### Update shelter capacity
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/shelters/1/capacity
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

25